snippet.title: Arena Breakout: Infinite Season 1 | Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Ladies and Gentlemen, welcome to watch Kamona TV.

Season 1 Update is officially set on Nov. 20th! 
Make sure to

✅Explore all-new TV Station & Armory Expansion Map
✅Test your skills with our brand new arsenal of weapons
✅Join Fog, Storm and other exclusive seasonal events. 
🎁Claim Seasonal special bonus and free skins

🔗 Try the brand new extraction shooter at arenabreakoutinfinite.com

#ArenaBreakoutPC #ArenaBreakoutInfinite #ABIS1
